---
title: Crispy Turkey Breast Parmigiana with Baby Spinach and Italian Bell Pepper Salad
description: The best part of this turkey parmigiana is the layer of crispy cheese on top! Each bite is crispy, salty and cheesy. Served with tender Italian-seasoned bell peppers and perfectly dressed spinach, dinner tonight is simple and refined!

